#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.elliprc.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.elliprc"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:1 of
msgid "Degenerate symmetric elliptic integral."
msgstr "退化的对称椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:3 of
msgid "The function RC is defined as [1]_"
msgstr "函数 RC 定义为 [1]_"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:5 of
msgid ""
"R_{\\mathrm{C}}(x, y) =\n"
"   \\frac{1}{2} \\int_0^{+\\infty} (t + x)^{-1/2} (t + y)^{-1} dt\n"
"   = R_{\\mathrm{F}}(x, y, y)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.elliprc.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:11
#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:14 of
msgid ""
"Real or complex input parameters. `x` can be any number in the complex "
"plane cut along the negative real axis. `y` must be non-zero."
msgstr ""
"实数或复数输入参数。`x` 可以是沿负实轴切割的复平面上的任意数。`y` 必须"
"非零。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:17 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function values"
msgstr "函数值的可选输出数组"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.elliprc.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:20 of
msgid ""
"**R** -- Value of the integral. If `y` is real and negative, the Cauchy "
"principal value is returned. If both of `x` and `y` are real, the return "
"value is real. Otherwise, the return value is complex."
msgstr ""
"**R** -- 积分值。如果 `y` 是实数且为负，则返回柯西主值。如果 `x` 和 `y` "
"都是实数，则返回值为实数。否则，返回值为复数。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.elliprc.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:27 of
msgid ":py:obj:`elliprf`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:28 of
msgid "Completely-symmetric elliptic integral of the first kind."
msgstr "第一类完全对称椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:30 of
msgid ":py:obj:`elliprd`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:31 of
msgid "Symmetric elliptic integral of the second kind."
msgstr "第二类对称椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:33 of
msgid ":py:obj:`elliprg`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:34 of
msgid "Completely-symmetric elliptic integral of the second kind."
msgstr "第二类完全对称椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:36 of
msgid ":py:obj:`elliprj`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:37 of
msgid "Symmetric elliptic integral of the third kind."
msgstr "第三类对称椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:40 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:41 of
msgid ""
"RC is a degenerate case of the symmetric integral RF: ``elliprc(x, y) == "
"elliprf(x, y, y)``. It is an elementary function rather than an elliptic "
"integral."
msgstr ""
"RC 是对称积分 RF 的退化情况：``elliprc(x, y) == elliprf(x, y, y)``。它是"
"一个初等函数，而不是椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:45 of
msgid ""
"The code implements Carlson's algorithm based on the duplication theorems"
" and series expansion up to the 7th order. [2]_"
msgstr "代码实现了基于倍增定理和级数展开至第 7 阶的 Carlson 算法。[2]_"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:49 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:50 of
msgid ""
"B. C. Carlson, ed., Chapter 19 in \"Digital Library of Mathematical "
"Functions,\" NIST, US Dept. of Commerce. https://dlmf.nist.gov/19.16.E6"
msgstr ""
"B. C. Carlson 编，《数学函数数字图书馆》第 19 章，NIST，美国商务部。https"
"://dlmf.nist.gov/19.16.E6"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.elliprc:53 of
msgid ""
"B. C. Carlson, \"Numerical computation of real or complex elliptic "
"integrals,\" Numer. Algorithm, vol. 10, no. 1, pp. 13-26, 1995. "
"https://arxiv.org/abs/math/9409227 https://doi.org/10.1007/BF02198293"
msgstr ""
"B. C. Carlson, \"实数或复数椭圆积分的数值计算,\" Numer. Algorithm, 第 10 "
"卷, 第 1 期, pp. 13-26, 1995. https://arxiv.org/abs/math/9409227 https://"
"doi.org/10.1007/BF02198293"

